# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this projectadheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]
### Added
- Nothing.

### Changed
- Switched to [guile hall][guile-hall] and [autotools][autotools] based
  workflow.

### Removed
- Nothing.

## [0.1.0]
### Added
- `lwarpmk` is now used to provide HTML output of project, allowing hosting of
  papers easily online.
- `localtest.sh` will load the library and executable to allow changes to be
  tested independently of environment.
- `.projectile` file generation added.
- `-h` and `-v` flags print version and help information.
- Ability to skip `.metadata` and `.projectile` file generation with appropriate
  flags.

### Changed
- Default CSS currently points to self-hosted CSS file on https://cdr255.com/
- Font used is now [Gyre Termes][gyre-termes].

### Removed
- Empty List in Tests.

## [0.0.1]
### Added
- Initial Project Files.
- Org-based Project Structure.
- Will actually compile a PDF correctly.

### Changed
- README is now accurate to script use.

### Removed
- Unneeded temporary files from git repo.

[0.1.0]: https://git.sr.ht/~yewscion/genpro/refs/v0.1.0
[0.0.1]: https://git.sr.ht/~yewscion/genpro/refs/v0.0.1
[Unreleased]: https://git.sr.ht/~yewscion/genpro/log
[gyre-termes]: https://ctan.org/pkg/tex-gyre-termes?lang=en
